                  </persName>
            , Q. You keep the house, No. 4, Baldwin's-place, Baldwin's-gardens - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you remember a press being brought to your house in February last - A. I believe it was about that time. It was placed in the two pair back room. 
               <persName id="t18130915-50-person482">
