             agreed with me for that room. It was taken away on a Sunday morning. I did not know any of the persons. I was paid three shillings for two weeks.</p>
               <p>Q. During the time the press was in your house do you remember seeing the prisoner there - A. Not to my knowledge. I saw a young man there once.</p>
               <p>Q. Look at the prisoner, is that the person - A. Yes, that is the person. I did not know whether he belonged to it or not. I remember his coming there.</p>
               <p>Q. Had he any thing else there to do; was he a lodger there - A. No, not at all.</p>
